@page
@model AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<section class="hero-section" aria-labelledby="about-hero-heading">
    <div class="decorative-scoop" aria-hidden="true">🍦 🤎 🍨 🌿 🍧</div>
    <h1 id="about-hero-heading" class="display-4">About Froyo Foundry</h1>
    <p class="lead">Where passion meets frozen yogurt — one perfect scoop at a time.</p>
</section>

<section class="froyo-card" aria-labelledby="mission-heading">
    <span class="mission-eyebrow" id="mission-heading">Our Mission</span>
    <h2 class="froyo-heading">Delighting Every Customer</h2>
    <p>
        At Froyo Foundry, we believe frozen yogurt is more than a treat — it's a moment of joy.
        Our mission is to craft delicious, high-quality frozen yogurt experiences that bring people
        together, celebrate community, and put a smile on every face.
    </p>
    <p>
        We are committed to <strong>quality ingredients</strong>, <strong>warm hospitality</strong>,
        and constantly listening to our customers to make every visit better than the last.
    </p>
    <blockquote class="mission-quote">
        "Life is better with a scoop in your hand and good people by your side."
    </blockquote>
</section>

<section aria-labelledby="founder-heading">
    <h2 id="founder-heading" class="froyo-heading mb-4">Meet the Founder</h2>
    <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="founder-portrait">
                <div class="founder-portrait-emoji" aria-hidden="true">🍦</div>
                <div class="founder-name">Michael Collier</div>
                <div class="founder-title">Founder &amp; Flavor Champion</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <p>
                <strong>Michael Collier</strong> founded Froyo Foundry with a simple idea: that great food,
                like great people, should be celebrated every day. A proud <strong>Ohio State Buckeyes</strong>
                fan through and through, Michael carries the Buckeye spirit of hard work, community, and
                never giving up into everything he does.
            </p>
            <p>
                When he's not perfecting a new flavor, you'll find Michael at the grill — a dedicated
                <strong>BBQ enthusiast</strong> who believes low-and-slow patience is just as important
                in business as it is in barbecue. His love of craft and process shows in every detail at
                Froyo Foundry.
            </p>
            <p>
                An <strong>avid golfer</strong>, Michael knows that consistency, practice, and staying calm
                under pressure are the keys to a great round — and a great business. He brings that same
                steady focus to building a brand customers can count on.
            </p>
            <p>
                Above all, Michael is a <strong>family man</strong>. The values instilled by his family —
                generosity, laughter, and showing up for one another — are the heart of Froyo Foundry's culture.
                Every customer who walks through our doors is welcomed like family.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="mt-5" aria-labelledby="passions-heading">
    <h2 id="passions-heading" class="froyo-heading mb-4">Passion in Every Scoop</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Michael's personal passions aren't just hobbies — they're the DNA of Froyo Foundry.</p>
    <div class="row g-3">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
            <div class="passion-card">
                <div class="passion-card-emoji" aria-hidden="true">🏈</div>
                <h3>Buckeye Pride</h3>
                <p>Team spirit and community loyalty inspire us to root for our neighbors and celebrate wins together.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
            <div class="passion-card">
                <div class="passion-card-emoji" aria-hidden="true">🔥</div>
                <h3>BBQ Craft</h3>
                <p>The patience and care of great barbecue guides how we develop every flavor — slowly, thoughtfully, with love.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
            <div class="passion-card">
                <div class="passion-card-emoji" aria-hidden="true">⛳</div>
                <h3>Golfer's Focus</h3>
                <p>One shot at a time. We focus on the details that matter so every customer experience is on par — or better.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">
            <div class="passion-card">
                <div class="passion-card-emoji" aria-hidden="true">❤️</div>
                <h3>Family Values</h3>
                <p>A family-first mindset means we treat everyone who visits Froyo Foundry with warmth, respect, and a big smile.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="about-cta mt-5">
    <h2>Ready to Taste the Difference?</h2>
    <p>Come experience the flavor, the warmth, and the Froyo Foundry difference for yourself.</p>
    <a asp-page="/Order" class="froyo-btn-primary">Place an Order</a>
</div>
